# Project: Agentic Scrum Assistant (Cursor Buildathon — May 16)

## What We Are Building
A standalone an Agentic Scrum Assistant that automates repetitive tracking and communication across an Agile Scrum team. NOT built on top of any existing PM platform. Integrates with Plane Cloud via REST API. All user-facing orchestration in n8n (track technology).

## Directory Structure
```
.                               # Root — standalone project root
├── backend/                    # Python FastAPI backend
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── api/endpoints/      # FastAPI route handlers
│   │   ├── core/               # Config, auth, DB session
│   │   ├── model/              # Pydantic models
│   │   ├── service/            # Business logic (plane, github, memory)
│   │   ├── database.py         # Supabase async connection
